chemaxon.marvin.common

Class ParameterConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • chemaxon.marvin.common.ParameterConstants
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SketchParameterConstants, ViewParameterConstants

    public class ParameterConstants
extends Object
    Parameters of Marvin Applets and Beans. The parameters of the JMSketch and JMView applets can be set using the <param> HTML tag. The parameters of the MSketchPane and MViewPane JavaBean components can be set using the setParams method.
    Since:
    Marvin 5.2
    Version:
    5.2.2, 05/04/2009
    Author:
    Eva Hollo, Judit Vasko-Szedlar
